data.title: Elisabeth Franziska Maria von Habsburg ...
data.meta_description: Royalty, Archduchess of Austria. She married Ferdinand Karl of Austria-Este and gave birth to a daughter. Her husband died five months later. In 1854 she married another of her cousins, Karl Ferdinand of Austria. Following her last will she was buried in Baden, where she had spent large parts of her later life.
